: 36}, "passed": true}}, "text": "Taiwan Strait Situation (as of 0100 EDT, 1 September):\nWith the exception of renewed and apparently heavy shelling of Tungting, a small island south of Kinmen (Quemoy), on 31 August, there has been a general lull", "token_count": 36, "token_end_0based": 43, "token_start_0based": 8, "token_text": "taiwan strait situation as of 0100 edt 1 september with the exception of renewed and apparently heavy shelling of tungting a small island south of kinmen quemoy on 31 august there has been a general lull", "unred_source_page": 4}
